{"tid":2416880,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"嘩𨳒！初七強制使用「安心」出行後，新增確診爆升149% 比疫情高峰時升幅還要幾何級多！","createTime":"2021-02-21T11:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T17:13:46.000Z","uid":359029,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ccf47f3054140b6b8fae61d28fa24c4da414fd51","tid":2416880,"uid":359029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T11:58:37.000Z","msg":"DLLM 初七個政府放寬了限制後，才三天今日個新增確診數字狂爆，狂升超過149% 應該相比任何階段的升幅都明顯為多，完全係 significant surge...<br />\n<br />\n點解有安心出行都可以錄得如此巨大升幅。<br />\n可以理解為安心出行是垃圾一樣？<br />\n一定係，除非唔係。<br />\n<br />\n我認為呢個近兩倍半嘅驚人升幅：<br />\n<br />\n本人認為情況極不理想。 其實推強制安心出行，果班垃圾，是不是應該不好再厚顏無恥地，戀棧權力，問責下台，讓有能之士居之！"},{"pid":"b594dc4651739f688f6c5fda3825f3603b58d9ef","tid":2416880,"uid":280593,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:35:30.000Z","msg":"又話裝左app免疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"149f9ec9c874cfe539f82d03852f829e02c7aec3","tid":2416880,"uid":359029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b594dc4651739f688f6c5fda3825f3603b58d9ef","tid":2416880,"uid":280593,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:35:30.000Z","msg":"又話裝左app免疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:42:17.000Z","msg":"政府好明顯冇insight"},{"pid":"5ab1c374d78a9e1a6f6da3affc4c6a13c393b8a8","tid":2416880,"uid":2924,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T13:03:45.000Z","msg":"冇晒反對派, 又有國安法同安心出行, 又全民檢測, 點解仲係爆發架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e578d1d8fb554c020f6abc202ef5c0dc007ef70","tid":2416880,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"149f9ec9c874cfe539f82d03852f829e02c7aec3","tid":2416880,"uid":359029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b594dc4651739f688f6c5fda3825f3603b58d9ef","tid":2416880,"uid":280593,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy